FBIS4-35824 "drnes108dd_94015" FBIS-NES-94-108 Daily Report 6 Jun 1994 Palestinian Affairs Hamas Calls For More `Anti-Zionist' Operations Hamas Calls For More `Anti-Zionist' Operations NC0606054094 Tehran Voice of the Islamic Republic of Iran First Program Network in Persian 0330 GMT 6 Jun 94 NC0606054094 Tehran Voice of the Islamic Republic of Iran First Program Network Persian BFN [Text] The Islamic Resistance Movement Hamas has stated that it will intensify its anti-Zionist operations. In a statement issued yesterday, Hamas once again condemned the accord between the PLO and the Zionist regime and called on its combatants to intensify their anti-Zionist operations. Hamas also called on the Palestinians in the occupied territories to go on a general strike on Thursday [9 June], the 79th month of the Palestinians' uprising.
